    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. When you say 'flawless' and 'undistracting,' could you be more specific about hairstyles? For example, if someone has more natural or textured hair, or if they prefer styles that aren't strictly 'slicked back,' how should they approach that to make sure they aren't seen as less professional in those boardroom settings?",
